thread.title: BRIEF-Ctac extends partnership with Winshuttle to Belgium and France
thread.title_full: BRIEF-Ctac extends partnership with Winshuttle to Belgium and France | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Ctac extends partnership with Winshuttle to Belgium and France
text:
Sept 8 Ctac NV :
* Extends partnership with Winshuttle to Belgium and France
* The partnership means that Ctac's will deliver and support Winshuttle's data management platform in Belgium and France, as it does in the Netherlands Source text: bit.ly/1EMjH6m Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
